{"tid":953082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港兩大失控怪物：港鐵、領展","createTime":"2018-12-23T15:57:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T07:14:54.000Z","uid":221813,"like":813,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"0d07082bdc19463c8e12c63c46dbd805a9753c4a","tid":953082,"uid":221813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T15:57:13.000Z","msg":"兩個機構明明都係政府搞出黎，但上市後就愈來愈不受控制，仿佛淨賺錢賺到盡係第一位<br />\n<br />\n港鐵年年賺撈埋地產賺天文數字，但就年年加價，壞車工程出事鑊鑊金。加埋ok馬時亨管治下猶如獨立王國，政府都唔撚比面你<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n領展變賣公屋商場停車場資產，瘋狂加租迫走小商戶，變清一色鏈鎖倒模商場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 車位天價租金<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 街市賣比財團操控市場<br />\n<br />\n一句要顧及股東利益政府都吹佢唔脹，班19管理層袋天價花紅，衰過吸血鬼。係咪香港人都係揸番十手八手66，823對沖番先不至於住人魚肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cfb0829024f1fafc859eac0e610876256658027","tid":953082,"uid":180206,"like":59,"dislike":3,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T15:58:24.000Z","msg":"制裁佢地"},{"pid":"4117775e59064385cf4fded05918183d4b7b53e3","tid":953082,"uid":22675,"like":38,"dislike":156,"score":-118,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T15:59:10.000Z","msg":"係地鐵同領匯"},{"pid":"f7852ccac2f406c49a5da19557ebc20807f275c9","tid":953082,"uid":68728,"like":14,"dislike":60,"score":-46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T16:00:45.000Z","msg":"港鐵股價唔識升 咁都叫失控?"},{"pid":"287d39cee35dc87270a9f7efd34133a2ffdee979","tid":953082,"uid":96453,"like":87,"dislike":5,"score":82,"quote":{"pid":"4117775e59064385cf4fded05918183d4b7b53e3","tid":953082,"uid":22675,"like":38,"dislike":156,"score":-118,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T15:59:10.000Z","msg":"係地鐵同領匯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T16:02:00.000Z","msg":"講緊公司名ar ching"},{"pid":"6fa4ce43b9deb92d2726dd5e2e375dfe11bb69de","tid":953082,"uid":76753,"like":133,"dislike":0,"score":133,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T16:05:14.000Z","msg":"你第一句已經指出失控源頭"},{"pid":"56ca938c30ef0cc8302a9bba