lyTime":"2018-12-24T01:24:16.000Z","msg":"係 最好笑係823要賣商場 啲人又反對 到底係想要823 定唔想要？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結果823賣完 下手業主加租加得仲狠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6097b1d7fc17583610390dacf3d8d80fe01bd2a","tid":953082,"uid":174498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d07082bdc19463c8e12c63c46dbd805a9753c4a","tid":953082,"uid":221813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T15:57:13.000Z","msg":"兩個機構明明都係政府搞出黎，但上市後就愈來愈不受控制，仿佛淨賺錢賺到盡係第一位<br />\n<br />\n港鐵年年賺撈埋地產賺天文數字，但就年年加價，壞車工程出事鑊鑊金。加埋ok馬時亨管治下猶如獨立王國，政府都唔撚比面你<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n領展變賣公屋商場停車場資產，瘋狂加租迫走小商戶，變清一色鏈鎖倒模商場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 車位天價租金<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 街市賣比財團操控市場<br />\n<br />\n一句要顧及股東利益政府都吹佢唔脹，班19管理層袋天價花紅，衰過吸血鬼。係咪香港人都係揸番十手八手66，823對沖番先不至於住人魚肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T01:26:45.000Z","msg":"其實而家狗鐵情況係山頭太多、各自勢力都好穩固，變相要做改革或者其他嘢都好困難。呢一點無論係咪馬時亨做主席都係暨定事實。<br />\n<br />\n另外，如果政府放鳩晒手上啲地鐵股票，咁先至大鳩鍋<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f370110dc01ae697dbff737fb036da3fb073d0","tid":953082,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c31a6ae599174abbe0be3aae6e0d0a5db9564216","tid":953082,"uid":15548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"84e27739d5ae98a0530f6d20230e62c9ba2a4691","tid":953082,"uid":38523,"like":4,"dislike":15,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"5cacd08c2214c2f7c4de9fdaa8f3e3fd055cb712","tid":953082,"uid":15548,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T16:46:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a0Eknwy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa0Eknwy.png&h=0d4efe4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一行係你啲老闆呀"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T16:47:20.000Z","msg":"關狗咪你老闆